reviewText: My grandson LOVES the old Tom and Jerry shows!!  :)
More good cartoons for our collection!

This DVD contains six episodes from the Tom & Jerry Cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Mucho Mouse
2. It's Greek to Me-Ow
3. Tomb It May Concern
4. Zent out of shape
5. You're Lion
6. Kangadoofus
